{"word":"Forty","slug":"forty","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Forty</b> Remarkable coincidences in the number<br/> - Days:<br/> b of rain, at the time of the flood<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=7&verse=17'>Gen 7:17</a><br/> b of flood, before sending forth the raven<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=8&verse=6'>Gen 8:6</a><br/> b for embalming<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=50&verse=3'>Gen 50:3</a><br/> b of fasting:<br/> b by Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=18'>Exo 24:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=28'>Exo 34:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=9'>Deu 9:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=25'>Deu 9:25</a><br/> b by Elijah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=8'>1Ki 19:8</a><br/> b by Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=2'>Mat 4:2</a><br/> b Spies in the land of promise<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=25'>Num 13:25</a><br/> b of probation, given to the Ninevites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=3&verse=4'>Jon 3:4</a><br/> b Christ's stay after the resurrection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=3'>Act 1:3</a><br/> b Symbolic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=4&verse=6'>Eze 4:6</a><br/> - Years:<br/> b Wanderings of the Israelites in the wilderness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=16&verse=35'>Exo 16:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=34'>Num 14:34</a><br/> b Peace in Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=3&verse=11'>Jdg 3:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter